{"word":"G3525 - νήφω - nḗphō - nay'-fo - Be sober","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">νήφω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>nḗphō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>nay'-fo"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Be sober"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - தெளிந்தவர்களாயிரு, புத்தியுள்ளவர்களாயிரு, மனத்தெளிவுள்ளவனாயிரு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to be sober"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> Of uncertain affinity; to <i>abstain</i> from wine (<i>keep sober</i>), that is, (figuratively) <i>be discreet:</i> - be sober, watch."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1594 - ἐκνήφω - eknḗphō - ek-nay'-fo/1594\">G1594</a>, <a href=\"#/G3524 - νηφάλεος - nēpháleos - nay-fal'-eh-os/3524\">G3524</a>, <a href=\"#/G3525 - νήφω - nḗphō - nay'-fo/3525\">G3525</a>"}]}